{"tid":2341683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啲磚家擺明講大話，呃人疫苗對變種病毒同樣有效，明明零證據","createTime":"2020-12-26T14:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T14:31:43.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"876e8af25308f4bf84a492b0572d855a1777fa88","tid":2341683,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:31:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2923791211190284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2923791211190284&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=813d7bcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2923791211190284</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃鵹<br />\n<br />\n啲磚家擺明講大話，呃人疫苗對變種病毒同樣有效，明明零證據，真係唔知邊個反科學。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2923801454522593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2923801454522593&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=f1e54088\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2923801454522593</a><br />\n<br />\nPfizer/Moderna 係針對 spike protein。冇利益衝突嘅專家話 B.1.1.7 變種令 spike protein 形狀變咗，所以肯定有影響。但佢哋又亂舉流感疫苗做例子，話就算有 mismatch 都可以減少嚴重病症。癡撚線，牛津疫苗同流感疫苗先係同原理、可比較，P/M 完全冇研究過。唔知就應該講唔知。"}]}